    dc:creator "Kim, Wonwoong; Weele, Ruud Van Der; Lee, Seunghwan" ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "New records of Micropezidae (Diptera, Acalyptratae) from South Korea, with description of a new species of Rainieria Rondani" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021830>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021832>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021836>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021840>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021844> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021830>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Rainieria tenebrosa, live individuals. A, female; B, male; C, mating pair, with smaller male; D, mating pair, with smaller female; E, bubbling behavior of female during copulation; F, fluid exchange during copulation; G, male waving the intruder away during copulation; H, ‘aggregation oviposition’ on a bark of Quercus cf. dentata Thunb. [Figure D provided by Jae Seok Oh (SNU)]" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7021830/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021832>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lateral habitus and spermathecae of Rainieria species. A, Rainieria calceata, male; B, ditto, female; C, Rainieria triseta, male; D, ditto, female; E, Rainieria tenebrosa, holotype male; F, ditto, paratype female; G, ditto, spermathecae and associated structures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7021832/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021836>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Male genital structure of Rainieria species. A, D: Rainieria triseta; B, E: Rainieria tenebrosa; C, F: Rainieria calceata. A–C, Male Sternite V (Genital fork); D–F: Various structures of male terminalia. Abbreviations: aa—phallapodeme; bd—basal distiphallus; c—cercus; dd—distal distiphallus; e—epandrium; ea—ejaculatory apodeme; ed—ejaculatory duct; h—hypandrium; pb—phallic bulb." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7021836/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021840>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Female sternite structure of Rainieria species. A, Rainieria calceata; B, Rainieria tenebrosa; C, Rainieria triseta; D, ditto, ventral view of alcohol-preserved specimen. Note the reduction of sternite III–IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7021840/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7021844>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Wings of Korean Micropezidae species. A, Micropeza soosi; B, Compsobata dentigera; C, Rainieria triseta; D, Rainieria tenebrosa; E, Mimegralla suzukiana." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7021844/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

